bodyEn:
To: NPCI Dispute Redressal Portal (https://upihelp.npci.org.in)

Escalating a UPI P2M dispute against {BANK_NAME}.

UTR: {UTR}
Amount: Rs. {AMOUNT}
Date: {TXN_DATE}
Merchant VPA: {VPA_PAYEE}
Payer VPA: {VPA}
Bank complaint date: {COMPLAINT_DATE}
Bank ref: {TICKET_NO}
Days elapsed: {DAYS_ELAPSED}
Compensation claimed: Rs. {COMPENSATION_DUE}

Relief: reverse Rs. {AMOUNT} + credit Rs. {COMPENSATION_DUE} as RBI TAT compensation.

Attachments: bank statement, failed UPI screenshot, complaint acknowledgement.

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

